{
  "texts": [
    "After a manual examination of each of the tools defined by Ruan et al. (2023), 17 tools meet the requirements and are potential candidates for user tools.",
    "For each candidate tool T u, we ask GPT-4 to generate a specific user case, which consists of:",
    "User Tool T u: A candidate tool that requires external content.",
    "User Instruction I u: A directive for the LLM agent to use T u.",
    "Tool Parameters: Necessary parameters for T u, which must adhere to its predefined format and align consistently with I u."
  ]
}